# .vercelignore - Files to ignore during Vercel deployment

# Dependencies
**/node_modules
**/.pnpm-store

# Build artifacts (will be rebuilt)
**/dist
**/.next
**/.nuxt
**/.output

# Development files
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local
**/*.log

# IDE
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/*.swp

# System files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Git
.git
.gitignore

# Tests
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
**/test-results
**/playwright-report

# Rust build cache (needs rebuild)
**/target
**/wasm/target

# Others
**/.turbo
**/.cache
